race.comment: THE CATCH (1) loves this track and trip with two wins and two seconds from just five attempts. Drawn to get a gun run in transit from gate two and gets 3kg weight relief with the claim. Ticks a few boxes for a race of this calibre. FLYING BAT (2) is a two-time winner here who draws the inside marble with the claim. Can run a big race while fresh. CHASING JACKLEY (4) is a last-start victor who is another to get 3kg off. Include in calculations. CASTERLY ROCK (8) goes well for rider Thornton who has a win and four placings from nine rides. Ready to peak now third-up from the favourable draw and looks a must for the exotics.
